Overview
This repository houses the React Native frontend for a cutting-edge finance application that provides seamless access to modern financial services. The app integrates with a secure backend (built with PHP) to deliver features such as:

Virtual accounts
VTU purchases
Gift card transactions
Cryptocurrency trading
Engineered for performance and scalability, this frontend ensures a fast and intuitive user experience for mobile users while interacting with powerful API-driven backend services.

Key Features
Virtual Accounts
Real-time balance updates and transaction history.
Intuitive account management interface.
VTU Services
Easy airtime and data top-up with a clean UI.
Integration with multiple service providers for instant processing.
Gift Card Transactions
Smooth workflow for buying and redeeming gift cards.
Real-time pricing fetched dynamically from the backend.
Cryptocurrency Trading
User-friendly interface for buying, selling, and trading cryptocurrencies.
Dynamic pricing displayed in real time.
Interactive Dashboard
Visualizations of account balances, transaction summaries, and trading activity.
Designed for clarity and efficiency.
Technical Highlights
Cross-Platform Design: React Native ensures compatibility across Android and iOS devices.
API-Driven: Communicates with a robust backend via RESTful API endpoints.
Modern UI/UX: Built with reusable components and styled for a seamless user experience.
Real-Time Updates: Powered by API integration for instant feedback and data synchronization.
How It Works
User Authentication
Interacts with the backend for secure login and token-based sessions.
API Communication
Fetches data dynamically for virtual accounts, VTU, gift cards, and crypto services.
Dynamic Rendering
Optimized for smooth rendering of large data sets, including transaction histories and account details.
